    pageItem P92_ABSTRACT (
        type: richTextEditor
        label {
            label: <strong>Workshop Abstract</strong>
            alignment: left
        }
        settings {
            format: html
            minHeight: 220
            maxHeight: 220
        }
        layout {
            sequence: 240
            region: @workshop-details
            slot: regionBody
            alignment: left
        }
        appearance {
            template: @required-above
            templateOptions: #DEFAULT#
        }
        source {
            formRegion: @workshop-details
            column: ABSTRACT
            dataType: varchar2
        }
        default {
            type: static
            staticValue:
                ```
                <ul><li><b>Workshop Elevator Pitch/Messaging</b>:  Required </li>
                <li><b>Workshop Description</b>:  Required</li>
                <li><b>Why is this workshop needed?</b> Please fill in</li>
                <li><b>What products/technologies are used? </b> Please fill in</li>
                <li><b>Is there a primary Oracle product/technology being showcased?  If so, what is it? </b> Needed for Workshop Council</li>
                </ul>
                ```
        }
        security {
            encryptSessionState: false
        }
        help {
            inlineHelpText: Tell the Workshop Council about your workshop!
            helpText: This information is needed for approval.  Workshops are reviewed by the workshop council for adherance to current Oracle messaging
        }
    )

